title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Canada -  Cape Spear Lighthouse
description:
In this video we will fly over the Cape Spear Lighthouse. The Cape Spear Lighthouse is associated with the provisions of aid to navigation for the settlement of Newfoundland. Constructed in 1835, it was the first purpose-built lighthouse on the east coast of Newfoundland.
